title: Flight Simulator 2020 - How to - Find the correct Standard instrument departure
description:
For those who watched my video you probably have seen I am using SID's pretty regularly. From several of my subscribers I got the question how I select the correct SID's. 
In this how to I will show you how you can find more information about for standard instrument departures (SID's).
